stories.title: India v South Africa 3rd ODI - Statistical Highlights
stories.summary: It was the 1574th  ODI match in cricket history

stories.title: South Africans handled the pressure situation admirably
stories.summary: The Springboks were 0-2 down and it was a must win situation for them at Faridabad, to stay in the series

stories.title: Late rally by India fails after Kirsten, Cronje lay victory platform
stories.summary:
South Africa tried hard to make a simple task look difficult as they
beat India by 2 wickets with an over to spare in the third match of
the one-day series at the Nahar Singh Stadium in Faridabad today
